A research team led by Ram Babu Roy, assistant professor at Rajendra Mishra School of Engineering Entrepreneurship at IIT Kgp, has developed a prototype of sensor-based activity tracking kit which can monitor the activities in daily lives along with the smoking habits.A smartphone-based application is also underway that would analyse the tracking kit data and send alerts for unhealthy lifestyle with suitable recommendations.

